===Verb===
{{en-verb|lollygag|g|ed}}

# To [[dawdle]]; to be [[lazy]] or [[idle]]; to avoid necessary [[work]] or [[effort]].
#:''He was not about to tolerate such '''lollygagging''' on work time.''

